      <h1 class='about__heading about__heading--welcome'>Welcome!</h1>
      <p>SchoolBot is an open-source application that maps the locations of school buses. It is available to parents and guardians of students in participating school districts, and works on a wide variety of devices.</p>
      {{#scroll-to href='#districts' tagName='button' class='about__cta about__cta--learn'}}Learn more{{/scroll-to}}
